reviewText: Gave as a gift, and it was enjoyed. Vendor did well with shipping.
Bought this for Christmas present and my husband loves it!!!
Love it!  Met all my childs expectations!  I was even excited to see a wheelie stander that I saw personally when I was a young adult.
TOP NOTCH FILM that will be enjoyed by all who view it. You will not be disappointed!
I have always loved drag racing and cars in general.  It's amazing to watch these vehicles perform beyond what you would think possible.
Well edited and filmed, more action than you can shake a wheelie-bar at. Surely there's more footage of these wild machines for a part 2 ?

Loved the videos of the exhibition cars of the 70's and 80's. brought back lots of memories.
Also had video of Big Daddy after the Wacky Wheelie video. 2 for one video. Woo Hoo!
I remember most of these machines when they were new, and had hoped for a few more of them.  I did enjoy what there was, but it leaves you wishing there had been more.
